243
00:12:56,560 --> 00:12:57,560
Sudahlah! Cepat kejar!

244
00:13:06,320 --> 00:13:07,360
Ternyata begitu!

245
00:13:14,640 --> 00:13:16,080
Kalian sudah mengejar
