247
00:13:19,280 --> 00:13:20,200
Jangan lari lagi!

248
00:13:21,600 --> 00:13:22,720
Kenapa keras kepala sekali?

249
00:13:23,720 --> 00:13:26,320
Apa sepadan mengejar sampai
