256
00:13:40,960 --> 00:13:41,640
Orang kaya dengan emosi meledak-ledak.

257
00:13:41,720 --> 00:13:43,280
Sering berlintas-busana
dan diam-diam keluar istana.

258
00:13:43,360 --> 00:13:44,920
Orang-orang di dunia persilatan
memanggilnya Tuan Meng.

259
00:13:46,720 --> 00:13:49,760
